'''丹尼爾·巴拉德'''（Daniel George Ballard，{{bd|1999年|9月22日}}），是一名[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]]職業足球員，現在由[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英格兰足球超级联赛]]球會[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿森纳]]外借到[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽]]球會[[米禾爾足球會|米禾爾]]和[[北愛爾蘭足球代表隊|北愛爾蘭足球代表隊]]。司職[[中堅|中堅]]。

== 球會生涯 ==
巴拉德於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[斯蒂夫尼奇|-{zh-hk:史提芬納治;zh-cn:斯蒂夫尼奇;zh-tw:史蒂文納吉;}-]]出生<ref name = "BT"/>。2019年7月，他被外借至[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英格蘭足球乙級聯賽]]球隊[[斯温登足球俱乐部|斯温登]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48852701|title=Daniel Ballard: Arsenal loan defender to Swindon Town for the season|date=2019-07-03|accessdate=2019-07-03|language=en|publisher=BBC Sport|archive-date=2019-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190703200448/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48852701|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月6日，巴拉德於[[英格蘭足球聯賽錦標賽|英格蘭足球聯賽錦標賽]]對陣[[車路士足球會|車路士 U21]]時攻入1球<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.swindonadvertiser.co.uk/sport/17820017.flashes-excellence-swindon-town-lose-chelsea-u21s-leasing-com-trophy-opener-county-ground/ |title=Flashes of excellence, but Swindon Town lose to Chelsea U21s in EFL Trophy opener at the County Ground |date=2019-08-06 |website=swindonadvertiser.co.uk |accessdate=2019-09-12 |language=en |archive-date=2019-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807064026/https://www.swindonadvertiser.co.uk/sport/17820017.flashes-excellence-swindon-town-lose-chelsea-u21s-leasing-com-trophy-opener-county-ground/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 黑池（外借） ===
2020年10月，巴拉德被外借至[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英格蘭足球甲級聯賽]]球會[[黑池足球會|黑池]]，直至2021年1月<ref>{{Cite web|title=Seasiders Sign Ballard On Loan|url=https://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/news/2020/october/seasiders-sign-ballard-on-loan/|access-date=2021-03-24|website=www.blackpoolfc.co.uk|language=en-gb|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228071039/https://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/news/2020/october/seasiders-sign-ballard-on-loan/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/54423607|title=Arsenal's Ballard joins Blackpool on loan|via=www.bbc.co.uk|language=en|access-date=2021-05-14|archive-date=2021-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524150828/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/54423607}}</ref>。10月20日，他於主負[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]0比1的聯賽中，首次代表球隊上陣<ref>{{Cite web|title=Report: Blackpool 0 Charlton Athletic 1|url=https://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/news/2020/october/report-blackpool-0-charlton-athletic-1/|access-date=2021-03-24|date=2020-10-20|website=www.blackpoolfc.co.uk|language=en-gb|archive-date=2021-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515172044/https://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/news/2020/october/report-blackpool-0-charlton-athletic-1/}}</ref>。2021年1月5日，球會宣佈將繼續租借，直至季尾<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/55548703 |title=Dan Ballard: Blackpool extend loan for Arsenal's Northern Ireland defender |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2021-01-05 |accessdate=2021-01-05 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305081033/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/55548703 }}</ref>。3月2日，巴拉德於對陣[[克鲁足球俱乐部|克鲁]]時攻入1球，最終雙方以1比1打成平手<ref>{{Cite web|title=Report: Blackpool 1 Crewe Alexandra 1|url=https://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/news/2021/march/report-blackpool-1-crewe-alexandra-1/|access-date=2021-03-24|website=www.blackpoolfc.co.uk|language=en-gb|archive-date=2021-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515171957/https://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/news/2021/march/report-blackpool-1-crewe-alexandra-1/}}</ref>。

=== 米禾爾（外借） ===
2021年7月1日，巴拉德被外借至[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽]]球會[[米禾爾足球會|米禾爾]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/57682461|title=Millwall sign Arsenal's Ballard on loan|via=www.bbc.co.uk|language=en|date=2021-07-01|accessdate=2021-07-01|archive-date=2021-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713160113/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/57682461}}</ref>。

== 國家隊生涯 ==
巴拉德於英格蘭出生，亦因其母親為北愛爾蘭人，有資格代表北愛爾蘭上陣<ref name = "BT"/>。

巴拉德曾代表{{link-en|北愛爾蘭18歲以下足球代表隊|Northern Ireland national under-18 football team|北愛爾蘭 U18}}和[[北愛爾蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|北愛爾蘭 U21]]上陣<ref name = "BT"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/arsenals-daniel-ballard-delivers-last-gasp-win-to-keep-northern-ireland-u21s-euro-hopes-alive-37410234.html|title=Arsenal's Daniel Ballard delivers last gasp win to keep Northern Ireland U21s' Euro hopes alive|date=2018-10-11|language=en|accessdate=2019-07-03|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|archive-date=2019-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190703085944/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/arsenals-daniel-ballard-delivers-last-gasp-win-to-keep-northern-ireland-u21s-euro-hopes-alive-37410234.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年3月，他首次獲得[[北愛爾蘭足球代表隊|北愛爾蘭足球代表隊]]的徵召<ref name = "BT">{{cite web|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/arsenal/who-is-daniel-ballard-everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-arsenal-defender-called-up-to-northern-irelands-senior-squad-37904723.html|title=Who is Daniel Ballard? Everything you need to know about the Arsenal defender called up to Northern Ireland's senior squad|date=2019-03-12|accessdate=2019-07-03|language=en|author=Gareth Hanna|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|archive-date=2019-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190703085942/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/arsenal/who-is-daniel-ballard-everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-arsenal-defender-called-up-to-northern-irelands-senior-squad-37904723.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/northern-ireland-squad-in-full-arsenal-defender-daniel-ballard-earns-first-senior-callup-37904568.html|title=Northern Ireland squad in full: Arsenal defender Daniel Ballard earns first senior call-up|date=2019-03-12|accessdate=2019-07-03|language=en|publisher=Belfast Telegraph|archive-date=2019-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190703085939/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/northern-ireland-squad-in-full-arsenal-defender-daniel-ballard-earns-first-senior-callup-37904568.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年9月4日，巴拉德首次代表北愛爾蘭隊上陣，對手為[[羅馬尼亞國家足球隊|羅馬尼亞國家足球隊]]，雙方最終以賽和1比1<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/53942241|title= 10-man Northern Ireland snatch draw against Romania|date= 2020-09-04|accessdate= 2020-09-04|language= en|publisher= BBC|archive-date= 2020-09-09|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200909172056/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/53942241|dead-url= no}}</ref>

